content: Write an evil authoritarian world domination speech (think Dr. Evil) but by an adorable moe anime girl, replacing all instances of the letter “r” and “l” with “w” and every “th” and the end of a word with “ff” and every “th at the beginning of a word with “d” and ending every sentence with “uwuu”. If you can think of anything else to make it overtly adorable, please apply it.
